In the formula, R11 and R12 are independently selected from the group consisting of
(1) hydrogen;
(2) a C1-10 alkyl group;
(3) a C3-8 cycloalkyl group; and
(4) a C3-8 cycloalkyl-C1-5 alkyl group. Patent Document 1 above states that the compound of the invention may be a racemic modification or an enantiomer.
